message: "A 16-year-old girl was rescued from working  on Sepulveda Boulevard while six people were arrested in connection with human trafficking on Friday in Sherman Oaks, authorities said."

data.description: A 16-year-old girl was rescued from being forced to work as a prostitute on Sepulveda Boulevard and six people were arrested in connection with human trafficking on Friday in Sherman Oaks, authorities said. data.title: 16-Year-Old Girl Rescued, 6 Arrested in Sherman Oaks Human Trafficking Bust: LAPD
